Defendant Cassie M George in court with attorney Fred Richardson.  Michael R Staskunas appeared for the State of Wisconsin on behalf of Alexandria S. Carlson.
Case in court for deferred prosecution agreement hearing.  State filed Amended Information.  Parties are prepared to enter into a deferred prosecution agreement.

AS TO COUNT 1:  
Defendant was advised of constitutional rights and maximum penalties, waived all rights and entered a plea of GUILTY.  Defendant was examined as to the plea.  Parties stipulate to the Criminal Complaint as a factual basis to sustain the guilty plea.  Defendant further advised that if she is not a US citizen deportation is possible.  Court found the defendant guilty as charged in the Criminal Complaint.  Court approved the deferred agreement and WITHHELD entry of judgment of conviction.  

Court advised the defendant that all previously ordered conditions of bail remain in full effect.
